    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我理解为门户初始状态指向Safe，然后Safe可以触发EmergencyStop。那紧急停机之后能直接恢复吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safe",
        "EmergencyStop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，通过Reset操作回到Safe状态。但还要考虑一种中间状态——安全检查失败时先进入Warning，而不是直接停机。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safe",
        "Warning",
        "EmergencyStop",
        "Reset"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加Warning作为中间层。Safe在Safety Check Failed时转入Warning，Warning在Issue Resolved后回到Safe。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Safe",
        "Warning",
        "Safety Check Failed",
        "Issue Resolved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Warning还有一个出口：如果发生Critical Failure，必须直接进入EmergencyStop。另外，整个系统最终要优雅地关闭到GradeSync模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Warning",
        "EmergencyStop",
        "Critical Failure",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，EmergencyStop触发System Shutdown后，流程终止在GradeSync节点？这是最终状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EmergencyStop",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "System Shutdown"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，System Shutdown是最终动作，GradeSync作为终点。还有E-Stop Triggered这个触发条件也要标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
